k\" id=\"widget0_subwidget1\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 2xl:px-0 items-start text-left\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 w-full items-start text-left\"><hgroup class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\"><h1 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-4\">392 AC</h1></hgroup><hr class=\"border-none bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-transparent via-primary-400 h-1\" style=\"width:0px\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"timeline\" id=\"widget0_subwidget2\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 px-4 2xl:px-0\"><ul class=\"grid grid-flow-row auto-rows-max grow\"><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">September</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Opening of the Solstice Gate and launch of the Rediscovery Endeavor beyond Asgartha<br/>\nThe Kraken is felled</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">October</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Securing of Oorun, the region directly adjacent to Asgartha<br/>\nThe Bravos fortress of the Cebir is reclaimed. Evidence of esoteric experimentation is found there</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">November</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Kojo receives the Carnelian Crown for his exploit against the Kraken<br/>\nProclamation of the Age of Rediscovery</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">December</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">The exploration of Oorun begins<br/>\nThe wreck of the Mesektet is recovered<br/>\nOorun is renamed Caer Oorun, as a rightful Asgarthan Province</p></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"content_block\" id=\"widget0_subwidget3\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 2xl:px-0 items-center text-center\"><div class=\"md-medium md:lg-medium text-neutral-800 flex flex-col w-full items-center text-center\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\"><img alt=\"clearskies-banner2 (1)\" data-nimg=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"100vw\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"color:transparent;width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"0\"/></p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"content_block\" id=\"widget0_subwidget4\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 2xl:px-0 items-start text-left\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 w-full items-start text-left\"><hgroup class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\"><h1 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-4\">393 AC</h1></hgroup><hr class=\"border-none bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-transparent via-primary-400 h-1\" style=\"width:0px\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"timeline\" id=\"widget0_subwidget5\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 px-4 2xl:px-0\"><ul class=\"grid grid-flow-row auto-rows-max grow\"><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">January</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">The Expeditionary Corps reach a snowy region they name the Storhvit.<br/>\nBelisenki attacks begin</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">February</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Exploration of the Storhvit and the Cais Adarra mountain range<br/>\nOpen conflict with the Belisenki</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">March</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">A Tumult hurricane threatens the exploration forces, prompting them to regroup at the center of the Oasis for protection<br/>\nDiscovery of the Mana Moths, the cornerstone of resolving the conflict with the Belisenki</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">April</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Discovery of the Nilam, a dead world-tree similar to the Spindle. Its crystallized trunk is the prison of an Oneiros: the dragon Kuraokami<br/>\nDiscovery of relics from a long-lost civilization. Among them is a new golden substance with clear energetic properties</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">May</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Kuraokami is freed by the Exalts, who redirect the power of the Tumult hurricane to shatter its jail<br/>\nThe Yzmir learn that Kuraokami was imprisoned by a powerful mage, who used the dragon’s power to unleash a catastrophic tsunami on Asgartha in 305 AC<br/>\nThe Storhvit is renamed Caer Nilam as it becomes a new Province of Asgartha<br/>\nJack Frost becomes the tutelary Oneiros of Caer Nilam, replacing Kuraokami in order to preserve the frozen ecosystem after the ice dragon’s release<br/>\nThe Ouroboros admiral ship locates the “City of Scholars”, 75 km north-northwest of the Cais Adarra</p></div></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>",
