medium text-neutral-800 flex flex-col w-full items-center text-center\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\"><img alt=\"Abyss2-banner\" data-nimg=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"100vw\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114244%2FAbyss2-banner.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114244%2FAbyss2-banner.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114244%2FAbyss2-banner.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114244%2FAbyss2-banner.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114244%2FAbyss2-banner.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114244%2FAbyss2-banner.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114244%2FAbyss2-banner.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114244%2FAbyss2-banner.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114244%2FAbyss2-banner.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"color:transparent;width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"0\"/></p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"content_block\" id=\"widget0_subwidget1\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 2xl:px-0 items-start text-left\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 w-full items-start text-left\"><hgroup class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\"><h1 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-4\">392 AC</h1></hgroup><hr class=\"border-none bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-transparent via-primary-400 h-1\" style=\"width:0px\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"timeline\" id=\"widget0_subwidget2\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 px-4 2xl:px-0\"><ul class=\"grid grid-flow-row auto-rows-max grow\"><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">Septembre</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Ouverture de la Porte du Solstice et lancement de l’Effort de Redécouverte hors d’Asgartha<br/>\nEradication du Kraken</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">Octobre</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Sécurisation d’Oorun, la région directement adjacente à Asgartha<br/>\nLa forteresse Bravos du Cebir est réinvestie. On y trouve des traces d’expérimentations ésotériques</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">Novembre</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Kojo reçoit la Couronne de Cornaline pour son exploit face au Kraken<br/>\nPromulgation de l’Âge de Redécouverte</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">Décembre</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Début de l’exploration d’Oorun<br/>\nL’épave de Mesektet est retrouvée<br/>\nOorun reprend le nom de Caer Oorun, en tant que Province d’Asgartha</p></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"content_block\" id=\"widget0_subwidget3\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 2xl:px-0 items-center text-center\"><div class=\"md-medium md:lg-medium text-neutral-800 flex flex-col w-full items-center text-center\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\"><img alt=\"clearskies-banner2 (1)\" data-nimg=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"100vw\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F05%2F26114449%2Fclearskies-banner2-1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"color:transparent;width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"0\"/></p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"content_block\" id=\"widget0_subwidget4\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 2xl:px-0 items-start text-left\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 w-full items-start text-left\"><hgroup class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\"><h1 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-4\">393 AC</h1></hgroup><hr class=\"border-none bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-transparent via-primary-400 h-1\" style=\"width:0px\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"timeline\" id=\"widget0_subwidget5\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 px-4 2xl:px-0\"><ul class=\"grid grid-flow-row auto-rows-max grow\"><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">Janvier</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Les Corps expéditionnaires foulent une région enneigée qu’ils nomment le Storhvit<br/>\nDébut des attaques belisenki</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">Février</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Exploration du Storhvit et de la chaîne de montagnes du Cais Adarra<br/>\nConflit ouvert avec les Belisenki</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">Mars</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Un ouragan de Tumulte menace les forces d’exploration, et elles décident de rallier le centre de l’Oasis pour se protéger<br/>\nDécouverte des Phalènes de Mana, pierre angulaire de la résolution du conflit avec les Belisenki</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">Avril</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Découverte du Nilam, un arbre-monde défunt, similaire au Fuseau. Son tronc cristallisé est la prison d’un Oneiros : le dragon Kuraokami<br/>\nDécouverte de reliques d’une société humaine défunte. Parmi elles, on trouve une nouvelle substance dorée aux propriétés énergétiques manifestes</p></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">Mai</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Kuraokami est libéré par les Exalts, qui détournent la puissance de l’ouragan de Tumulte pour briser sa prison<br/>\nLes Yzmir apprennent que Kuraokami a été enfermé par un mage puissant, qui a utilisé sa puissance pour lancer un tsunami dévastateur sur Asgartha en 305 AC<br/>\nLe Storhvit est rebaptisé Caer Nilam quand la région devient nouvelle Province d’Asgartha<br/>\nJack Frost devient l’Oneiros tutélaire de Caer Nilam, en remplacement de Kuraokami, afin de préserver l’écosystème gelé suite à la libération du dragon de froid<br/>\nL’Ouroboros, vaisseau amiral des Corps expéditionnaires, trouve la localisation de la “Cité des Sages”, à 75 km au nord-nord-ouest du Cais Adarra</p></div></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>",
